(define/contract (beautiful-substrings s k)
  (-> string? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let ([len (string-length s)])
    (define (vowel? c)
      (member c '(#\a #\e #\i #\o #\u)))
    (define (count-beautiful i j vowels consonants)
      (if (> i j)
          0
          (let* ([c (string-ref s i)]
                 [vowels (if (vowel? c) (+ vowels 1) vowels)]
                 [consonants (if (vowel? c) consonants (+ consonants 1))]
                 [next-count (count-beautiful (+ i 1) j vowels consonants)])
            (if (and (= vowels consonants) (= (modulo (* vowels consonants) k) 0))
                (+ 1 next-count)
                next-count))))
    (define (count-substrings i j)
      (if (> i len)
          0
          (if (> j len)
              (count-substrings (+ i 1) (+ i 2))
              (+ (count-beautiful i (- j 1) 0 0) (count-substrings i (+ j 1))))))
    (count-substrings 0 1)))
